		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者出场时携带3种<span textDecoration="underline">异界核心</span><span>，挂在其背后并逆时针转动，且按顺序</span><span fontWeight="normal">开启</span><span textDecoration="underline">元素护罩</span><span>，破盾后会有约</span><span color="#ffccbf">4s</span><span>的轻瘫时间，全破后重瘫</span><span color="#ffccbf">12s</span><span>。重瘫之后，会重新再生成3个核心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffacff">(雷元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者施放出3个连续的雷球，每个造成</span><span>50%,25%,10%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，若命中无护盾庇护的玩家，则产生</span><span textDecoration="underline">紫电</span><span color="#ffffff">的效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="405" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffacff">(雷元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者上肢拿着雷锥，一左一右地朝玩家丢过来，每个造成</span><span>70%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffacff">(雷元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者咏唱，朝玩家发射长激光，造成</span><span>100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="436" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999">(火元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者从地面上唤出4个火陨石，然后依次朝玩家扔过来，每个造成</span><span>80%,40%,16%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="436" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#7fbfff">(水元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者从地面上唤出4个水球，然后依次朝玩家扔过来，每个造成</span><span>80%,40%,16%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#99ffff">(冰元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">距离玩家比较近时，深罪浸礼者用碎冰壳包围自己，随后炸开，造成</span><span>100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1407" width="436" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#99ffff">(冰元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者从周围发射4个追踪冰锥，每个造成</span><span>78%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，若命中无护盾庇护的玩家，则产生</span><span textDecoration="underline">霜落</span><span color="#ffffff">的效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1407" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#99ffff">(冰元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者附魔</span><span>冰元素</span><span color="#ffffff">，然后朝玩家施放数刀冰刃，每个造成</span><span>50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，最后施放一刀十字冰刃，造成</span><span>70%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#7fbfff">(水元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者附魔</span><span>水元素</span><span color="#ffffff">，然后朝玩家施放数刀水刃，每个造成</span><span>50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，最后施放十字水刃，造成</span><span>70%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。若命中无护盾庇护的玩家，则产生</span><span textDecoration="underline">激流</span><span color="#ffffff">的效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="436" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999">(火元素盾)<span color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者在玩家处召唤7个地喷火，排成蜂巢状，每个造成</span><span>50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，若命中无护盾庇护的玩家，则产生</span><span textDecoration="underline">渊火</span><span color="#ffffff">的效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">核心数量<span color="#dfffbf">为剩余护罩数量</span><span>。深罪浸礼者将自己所剩的</span><span textDecoration="underline">核心</span><span>放置于地面，核心可摧毁，全摧毁后会重瘫；若未及时摧毁，其将在12s后全部爆炸，每个造成对应元素的</span><span color="#ffff99">200%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深罪浸礼者.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
