		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#8e1498" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8e1498">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1388" width="443" height="231" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">异界核心：深罪浸礼者出场携带核心顺序如下，每日轮换：<span color="#ff9999">火</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>，</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>，</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>，</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>。<br/>元素核心：</span><span color="#ff9999">2火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">2水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">2雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">2冻</span><span>盾，击毁可阻止其引爆，全部击毁可重瘫浸礼者。<br/>元素护罩：</span><span color="#ff9999">12火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">12水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，击破使其瘫痪，瘫痪或使其再次施放元素法阵会使盾量减半，至多减半2次。<br/></span><span color="#ffacff">紫电</span><span>：扣除前台角色20点元素能量，1s触发一次，特殊能量不受影响。<br/></span><span color="#ff9999">渊火</span><span>：施加「渊火烙印」，扣除全队角色生命值，大小为15%角色生命值+13.3%浸礼者攻击力。<br/></span><span color="#7fbfff">激流</span><span>：前台角色处在CD中的技能的CD增加6s，1s触发一次。<br/></span><span color="#99ffff">霜落</span><span>：扣除80点体力，3s内再次命中则扣除25点体力。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深罪浸礼者.assets/Image_27.png')" x="64" y="192" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
