		<RichText x="738" y="1631" width="439" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#dfffbf">护罩持续时间超时后(30s)<span color="#ffffff">，深罪浸礼者链接两个核心，并在前方分别产生2个对应的元素球</span><span color="#bfffbf">(左下右上)</span><span color="#ffffff">，片刻后爆炸，每个元素球造成对应元素的</span><span color="#ffff99">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，然后换至下一个元素护罩，技能施放期间无元素护罩庇护。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深罪浸礼者.assets/Image_53.png')" x="720" y="1546">
